{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_08_01",
  "title": "小美山愛 1話 そーっと、そーっと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "そーっと、そーっと……\nみんなが起きないように……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stealthily‚ stealthily…\nSo no one wakes up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5600.000000000001,
          "startTime": 6.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 8.7152151108
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 9.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～っ、良かった……\nこれで今夜も誰にも見つからずに――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa~‚ thank goodness…\nNow I can go without anyone seeing me tonight too――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1666667302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こんな夜更けにどこに行くんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where are you going so late at night?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1602254866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.7429921149
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "ひっ！？\n{user}さん、どうしてここに！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!?\n{user}-san‚ why are you here!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 23.3296585241
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺は、ちょっと飲み物でも買おうと……\nいや、俺のことはいい。愛こそどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was just going to buy a drink…\nNever mind me. What about you‚ Ai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2352786589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 30.1318354447
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、それは、その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that’s‚ uh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1318354447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "こんな夜遅くに出かけるつもりか？\nレッスンで疲れてるんだから、ゆっくり休んだ方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you going out this late?\nYou’re tired from practice. It’s better to get some rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 40.2062970478
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "……えーとですね……眠れないので\nちょっと北海道の夜風に当たろうかなーなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ well… I couldn’t sleep‚\nSo I thought I’d go out and enjoy the Hokkaido night breeze…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "寒くて余計目がさえそうだけど……\nまぁいい。なら、俺も付き合うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll probably just get cold and stay awake…\nWell‚ it’s fine. Then I’ll come with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 54.1384281476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　{user}さんこそ\nお仕事でお疲れなんですから、早く休んで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? But {user}-san‚\nYou’re tired from work‚ you should get some rest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 60.2450946808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "私のことなんて、これっぽっちもお気になさらず！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about me at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2450946808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "こんな夜更けに一人で出歩かせる訳にはいかないよ\n愛が行くなら俺も行く",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t let you wander around alone this late at night.\nIf you’re going‚ I’m going too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9469684296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 70.094686524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえいえ！　ここはぜひ、私一人で！\n一人で行かせて下さいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ no! I have to go alone!\nPlease let me go alone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3655893577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 75.5247543811
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "私一人で、全く、全然、大丈夫ですので！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m totally‚ completely fine on my own!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5247543811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 79.9623116493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……なんで、そんなに嫌がるんだ？\n微妙にへこむんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why are you so against it?\nYou’re kind of hurting my feelings…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "ああっ！　{user}さんが嫌とか\nそういう意味じゃ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! It’s not that I dislike {user}-san‚\nor anything like that…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.2654800863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 89.071159029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "私、{user}さんのこと、ものすご～く\n信頼してるんですから！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I trust {user}-san‚\nso much!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 94.842383496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あまり大声出さないでくれ。みんな起きちゃうから\n……本当は他に理由があるんだろ？　話してくれないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ don’t shout so loud‚ you’ll wake everyone up\n…You have another reason‚ don’t you? Won’t you tell me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 104.6135169189
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、{user}さんに\n隠しごとは出来ませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I guess I can’t\nkeep secrets from {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0650261826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "実は私……北海道に到着してから\n毎晩ラーメンの食べ歩きをしてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The truth is… ever since we arrived in Hokkaido‚\nI’ve been going on ramen crawls every night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにラーメンが食べたかったのか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You wanted to eat ramen that badly…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.012001292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 121.062001292
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違います！　実家のラーメン屋で\n味噌ラーメンをより美味しく改良しようと思ってて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no! It’s just that‚ at my family’s ramen shop‚\nwe’re thinking about improving the miso ramen recipe‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.2666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "札幌は味噌ラーメンの有名な店が多いからな\nなるほど、研究って訳か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sapporo has a lot of famous miso ramen shops\nI see‚ you’re doing research.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.900005595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 134.7103252412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "はい、といっても\n食べて気が付いたことをメモする程度なんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ but…\nI’m just taking notes on what I think after eating.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0666722616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_08_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "私は父のようなプロじゃありませんから\nでも、少しは役に立てるかもしれないと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not a professional like my dad‚ you know\nBut I thought I might be able to help out a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.1672490806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
